        "No mention of logging Onfido response latency distribution or error categories (timeout vs 4xx vs 5xx) — critical for distinguishing Onfido-side issues from network issues at 3am"
      ]
    },
    "metrics": {
      "coverage": "Baseline exists with kyc_checks_total and kyc_duration_histogram",
