        "recommendation": "No retry with backoff strategy mentioned. Add retry logic (1-2 retries with jitter) for transient errors (429, 503) and ensure 4xx client errors are NOT retried."
      },
      {
        "scenario": "Health endpoint checks Onfido reachability — Onfido blip causes platform to pull KYC service from load balancer",
        "handling": "partial",
        "recommendation": "Separate liveness from readiness probes. Liveness should check the service itself. Readiness can check Onfido. This prevents unnecessary restarts when only Onfido is degraded."
      }
