    "retry_config": "No retry logic mentioned. Transient Onfido failures (network blips, 429s, 503s) result in immediate user-facing errors. Recommend 1-2 retries with exponential backoff and jitter for idempotent GET/check operations.",
    "timeout_config": "5s timeout is reasonable given Onfido's documented p99 of 3s, providing ~2s headroom. Acceptable as-is.",
    "circuit_breakers": "None. This is the single highest-priority gap. Without a circuit breaker, Onfido degradation causes every in-flight request to consume a thread/connection for up to 5s, risking thread pool exhaustion and cascading failure in the KYC service itself.",
    "graceful_degradation": "None. The service has a binary mode: Onfido works → registration works; Onfido fails → registration fails. A 'pending_verification' state is the standard industry pattern for KYC services and is essential for meeting the stated SLA."
