      "details": "If pending_verification flow is added, a new status column or state will need a migration. Current synchronous-only design has no migration concerns."
    },
    "verdict": "NOT READY"
  },

  "escalations": [
    {
      "type": "infrastructure_gap",
      "issue": "SLA is mathematically unachievable without a fallback path",
      "reason": "Team promises 99.95% uptime but has a hard synchronous dependency on Onfido (99.9% SLA) with no degraded mode. At best, this service can achieve 99.9% — guaranteeing SLA breach. Implementing a pending_verification async path requires a message queue (new infrastructure) not in the current spec.",
      "routed_to": "Coach K"
    },
    {
      "type": "infrastructure_gap",
      "issue": "No circuit breaker on the sole external dependency",
